---
import Layout from '../../layouts/Layout.astro';
import { SITE } from '../../site.config';

const baw = SITE.projects[0];
---

<Layout title="Terms of Use - Bookmark All Windows" theme="baw">
  <div class="max-w-[800px] mx-auto px-6 py-10 relative z-10">

    <h1 class="text-[2rem] font-bold text-[var(--color-accent)] mb-2">Terms of Use & Disclaimer</h1>
    <p class="text-slate-500 mb-8 pb-4 border-b border-[#2e2e3a]">
      <strong class="text-slate-300">Bookmark All Windows</strong> - Browser Extension<br />
      Last Updated: January 3, 2026
    </p>

    <h2 class="text-slate-100 text-xl font-semibold mt-8 mb-4">1. Acceptance of Terms</h2>
    <p class="mb-4">By installing and using the "Bookmark All Windows" browser extension ("Extension"), you agree to be bound by these Terms of Use. If you do not agree, please do not install or use the Extension.</p>

    <h2 class="text-slate-100 text-xl font-semibold mt-8 mb-4">2. Description of Service</h2>
    <p class="mb-3">The Extension provides functionality to bookmark all tabs from all open browser windows into organized folders. The Extension:</p>
    <ul class="list-disc ml-6 mb-4 space-y-2">
      <li>Reads tab URLs and titles from open windows</li>
      <li>Creates bookmark folders in your browser's bookmark system</li>
      <li>Optionally closes browser windows upon user request</li>
    </ul>

    <h2 class="text-slate-100 text-xl font-semibold mt-8 mb-4">3. Disclaimer of Warranties</h2>
    <p class="uppercase font-semibold mb-3">The Extension is provided "as is" and "as available" without warranties of any kind, either express or implied, including but not limited to:</p>
    <ul class="list-disc ml-6 mb-4 space-y-2">
      <li>Implied warranties of merchantability</li>
      <li>Fitness for a particular purpose</li>
      <li>Non-infringement</li>
      <li>Accuracy or reliability of any information obtained through the Extension</li>
    </ul>

    <h2 class="text-slate-100 text-xl font-semibold mt-8 mb-4">4. Limitation of Liability</h2>

    <h3 class="text-orange-400 text-lg font-semibold mt-6 mb-3">4.1 No Liability for Data Loss</h3>
    <div class="bg-red-950/30 border border-red-500/40 rounded-lg px-4 py-3 mb-4">
      <strong class="text-red-400">THE DEVELOPER IS NOT RESPONSIBLE FOR:</strong>
      <ul class="list-disc ml-6 mt-2 space-y-1.5">
        <li>Any loss of browser tabs, windows, or browsing sessions</li>
        <li>Unexpected closure of browser windows or tabs</li>
        <li>Loss of unsaved work in any browser tab</li>
        <li>Any data loss resulting from browser crashes, system failures, or Extension malfunction</li>
        <li>Incomplete or failed bookmark operations</li>
      </ul>
    </div>

    <h3 class="text-orange-400 text-lg font-semibold mt-6 mb-3">4.2 User Responsibility</h3>
    <div class="bg-amber-950/30 border border-amber-500/40 rounded-lg px-4 py-3 mb-4">
      <strong class="text-amber-400">YOU ACKNOWLEDGE AND AGREE THAT:</strong>
      <ul class="list-disc ml-6 mt-2 space-y-1.5">
        <li>You are solely responsible for saving any important work before using the Extension</li>
        <li>The "Close All Other Windows" feature will permanently close browser windows without additional confirmation</li>
        <li>Closed tabs and windows cannot be recovered by the Extension</li>
        <li>You should verify that bookmarks were created successfully before closing any windows</li>
        <li>Browser session data, form inputs, and unsaved content in closed tabs will be lost</li>
      </ul>
    </div>

    <h3 class="text-orange-400 text-lg font-semibold mt-6 mb-3">4.3 General Limitation</h3>
    <p class="uppercase font-semibold mb-3">In no event shall the developer be liable for any:</p>
    <ul class="list-disc ml-6 mb-4 space-y-2">
      <li>Direct, indirect, incidental, special, consequential, or punitive damages</li>
      <li>Loss of profits, data, use, goodwill, or other intangible losses</li>
      <li>Damages resulting from your use or inability to use the Extension</li>
      <li>Unauthorized access to or alteration of your data</li>
    </ul>

    <h2 class="text-slate-100 text-xl font-semibold mt-8 mb-4">5. Browser Permissions</h2>
    <ul class="list-disc ml-6 mb-4 space-y-2">
      <li><strong class="text-slate-300">tabs</strong>: To read URLs and titles of open tabs</li>
      <li><strong class="text-slate-300">bookmarks</strong>: To create bookmark folders and entries</li>
    </ul>

    <h2 class="text-slate-100 text-xl font-semibold mt-8 mb-4">6. Privacy</h2>
    <ul class="list-disc ml-6 mb-4 space-y-2">
      <li>Does NOT collect any personal information</li>
      <li>Does NOT transmit any data to external servers</li>
      <li>Does NOT track your browsing activity</li>
      <li>Operates entirely locally within your browser</li>
    </ul>

    <h2 class="text-slate-100 text-xl font-semibold mt-8 mb-4">7. Third-Party Services</h2>
    <p class="mb-4">The Extension does not integrate with or rely on any third-party services.</p>

    <h2 class="text-slate-100 text-xl font-semibold mt-8 mb-4">8. Modifications to the Extension</h2>
    <p class="mb-4">The developer reserves the right to modify, suspend, or discontinue the Extension at any time without notice.</p>

    <h2 class="text-slate-100 text-xl font-semibold mt-8 mb-4">9. Indemnification</h2>
    <p class="mb-4">You agree to indemnify and hold harmless the developer from any claims, damages, losses, or expenses arising from your use of the Extension or violation of these Terms.</p>

    <h2 class="text-slate-100 text-xl font-semibold mt-8 mb-4">10. Governing Law</h2>
    <p class="mb-4">These Terms shall be governed by and construed in accordance with applicable laws, without regard to conflict of law principles.</p>

    <h2 class="text-slate-100 text-xl font-semibold mt-8 mb-4">11. Changes to Terms</h2>
    <p class="mb-4">The developer reserves the right to update these Terms at any time. Continued use of the Extension after any changes constitutes acceptance of the new Terms.</p>

    <h2 class="text-slate-100 text-xl font-semibold mt-8 mb-4">12. Contact</h2>
    <p class="mb-4">For questions about these Terms, please open an issue on the <a href={baw.repoUrl} target="_blank" rel="noopener" class="text-[var(--color-accent)] hover:underline">GitHub repository</a>.</p>

    <div class="bg-[#202027] border border-[#2e2e3a] rounded-xl p-6 mt-8">
      <h2 class="text-[var(--color-accent)] text-xl font-semibold mt-0 mb-4">📋 Summary (Plain Language)</h2>
      <ul class="list-none space-y-2 text-slate-400">
        {[
          'This extension helps you bookmark tabs from all windows at once',
          'We are NOT responsible if your tabs or windows close unexpectedly',
          'We are NOT responsible for any lost work or data',
          'Always save your work before using the "Close All Other Windows" feature',
          "The extension works entirely offline and doesn't collect any data",
          'Use at your own risk',
        ].map((item) => (
          <li class="pl-5 relative before:content-['•'] before:text-[var(--color-accent)] before:absolute before:left-0">{item}</li>
        ))}
      </ul>
    </div>

    <p class="mt-8 p-4 bg-[#26262e] rounded-lg text-center text-sm text-slate-300">
      <strong>By using this Extension, you acknowledge that you have read, understood, and agree to be bound by these Terms of Use.</strong>
    </p>

    <div class="mt-12 pt-6 border-t border-[#2e2e3a] text-center text-slate-500">
      <p>{SITE.author.copyright}</p>
    </div>

  </div>
</Layout>
